---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
import RecentPublications from "../components/RecentPublications.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body class="w-full max-w-screen-md mx-auto my-4 dark:bg-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300" >
    <Header />
    <main class="flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="px-4 md:px-16 flex flex-col gap-4 md:my-10">
        <h1>Welcome to My Digital Garden</h1>
          <p>
            This is my public notebook—a space where I grow ideas in the open.
            It’s part journal, part zine, part map. Some thoughts are half-formed,
            others are more rooted. Nothing here is final, and that’s the point.
          </p>

          <h2>🪐 Topics I’m Exploring</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>northstar</strong> – guiding values and long-term direction</li>
            <li><strong>reflections</strong> – personal insights and moments of clarity</li>
            <li><strong>bookshelf</strong> – quotes, notes, and thoughts on what I’m reading</li>
            <li><strong>spiritual</strong> – musings on meaning, mystery, and faith</li>
            <li><strong>leadership</strong> – thoughts on influence, management, and people</li>
            <li><strong>productivity</strong> – systems, habits, and doing better work</li>
            <li><strong>travel</strong> – memories and learnings from the places I’ve been</li>
            <li><strong>ux</strong> – product design, strategy, and user-centered thinking</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>🚀 Note Status Tags</h2>
          <p>Ideas here are tagged based on how developed they are:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Launching</strong> 🚀 – early thoughts, mostly raw and exploratory</li>
            <li><strong>Orbiting</strong> 🛰 – in development, with growing depth and connections</li>
            <li><strong>Beacon</strong> 🌠 – established ideas that guide and anchor other notes</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            Some ideas change, merge, or get retired. But all of them reflect
            what I’m thinking about right now.
          </p>
      </div>
	  <RecentPublications />
	      </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

